::Ramulus::

Ramulus growls as the Ark shakes with the attack, about to run ouside when 
Rhinox ran off to take care of it. He relaxes. If there was a problem, Rhinox 
would call for backup. He tenses up again as he hears Cyber Claw's scream 
down the hallway.

"Please exuse me," he says to Shadow Cat, Snow Tech, and Dracona, and runs 
off down the hallway.

He reches Cyber Claw, stopping near her. "Are you alright?" He says, looking 
at the screaming fembot in front of him.
